    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>radishes</strong> (as finely as you can)</p><p>Peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, and continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1716979464795-x200.jpg",
