          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken thighs </strong>to the pan and cook for 7-8 min on each side or until charred and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Once cooked through add the <strong>miso glaze </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until thickened slightly – these are your <strong>miso-glazed chicken thighs</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
